data.description: APPROVED SHORT SALE!!!  30-45 DAYS TO CLOSE!! A Spacious updated home in a quiet neighborhood with easy access to the local lakes & highways. Located on a large corner lot  Prepare to be amazed at w/ the newer hardwood floors throughout the main 2 levels of the home. The kitchen features painted cabinets, entrance to the backyard , stainless appliances, quartz countertops & updated backsplash. Some of the many features of the home include a sunken living room, updated windows, main bath, water heater & ca. The finished walk out basement has a wood burning fireplace, bar w/ bar stools, & 1/2 bath with laundry. Picture yourself relaxing on the patio grilling out and enjoying the spacious backyard. This is the home you have been waiting for!  This is a SHORT SALE. Seller says bring offer!!
